# Copyrighted ground-truth: extracted book text and source PDFs stay LOCAL, never committed.
cartridges/*/source/book*.txt
cartridges/*/source/*.pdf
cartridges/*/source/*.epub
# NOTE: captured skill outputs (*-out-*.md) are NOT ignored. They are the skill's OWN
# critiques (not copyrighted) and are the golden ground truth for the efficacy axes
# (E4 clean-restraint, E-ref off-domain). Committing them makes a fresh clone self-contained:
# their absence is NEVER-EVALUATED, not a FAIL, so they must ship with the repo.

# harness noise
**/stop_hook_fired.log
.claude/
cartridges/*/source/book.index.jsonl

# human-in-loop checkpoint ledgers (run artifacts, written by the Trident observability layer)
runs/
cartridges/*/runs/
